_sText:
Alright, heres a pretty basic map, modled around a Farm.  This is my first map made for any real gamemode, so i hope it turns out well.  
Any feedback is greatly appreciated.

*Update*
This is now beta 2, Beta 2 offers many improvement, the main one being the Terrorists have been given much more opportunity to win.  There is a whole new are which the Ts are free to take to make it to the barn.  Also many of the bushes you can walk through now and i added a few physics entities to keep it exciting.

Mattimeo310
